&lt;h4&gt;Passive Information gathering&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;passive-information-gathering&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#passive-information-gathering&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web app recon is the process of mapping an application’s endpoints, parameters, and behavior to understand its attack surface.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong recon focuses on logic and hidden functionality, not just running automated tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
